Creating a New Case
Login with your credentials

Navigate to "Cases" section

Click "Add New Case"

Fill in case details (title, priority, description)

Add relevant tags for categorization

Uploading Evidence
Select a case from the dropdown

Click "Upload Evidence"

Choose file(s) to upload

Add evidence type and tags

Review extracted metadata

Analyzing Evidence
Go to "Analysis" section

Select evidence to analyze

View extracted metadata

Use analysis tools (Hex view, String search)

Generate forensic report

Generating Reports
Navigate to "Reports" section

Click "Generate Report"

Select report format (PDF recommended)

Download or print the report

ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture
Frontend
Pure HTML/CSS/JavaScript - No framework dependencies

Responsive Design - Works on desktop and tablet

Modular Components - Reusable UI components

Security Features
CryptoJS for client-side encryption

EXIF.js for image metadata extraction

LocalStorage Encryption for data protection

Input Sanitization to prevent XSS

Data Management
Mock Database using localStorage

Encrypted Storage for sensitive data

Audit Trail for all operations

Backup & Restore capabilities
